title: Rupert Murdoch suggests Obama isn't 'real black president'
text: > Entertainment Rupert Murdoch suggests Obama isn't 'real black president' President Barack Obama participates in a conversation co-hosted by Coworker.org during the White House Summit on Worker Voice in the East Room of the White House in Washington, Wednesday, Oct. 7, 2015. Participants included workers, employers, unions, organizers and other advocates and experts on how to energize a new generation of Americans to come together and recognize the potential power of their voice at work. (AP Photo/Susan Walsh)
